Shane Smith:
<i>This week on "Vice,"</i>

00:08.370 --> 00:12.239
<i>the staggering surge of
incarcerated women in America.</i>

00:14.209 --> 00:16.076
<i>The overwhelming
majority of women</i>

00:16.111 --> 00:17.910
are there
for non-violent crimes.

00:19.881 --> 00:21.147
Your legs are
shackled to the bed.

00:21.182 --> 00:22.915
Yeung: Whilst the
C-section's happening?

00:22.951 --> 00:26.352
Like that's the point when you're
gonna run away. I know, right!

00:26.387 --> 00:28.587
Smith: <i>And then, how the
threat of forgeries</i>

00:28.623 --> 00:31.658
<i>is causing turmoil
in the art world.</i>

00:31.693 --> 00:34.192
Rainer Crone: Fantastic.
Ben Anderson: Same paint.

00:34.227 --> 00:36.161
Same acetate, same everything.

